org.microbean.kubernetes.controller.cdi

Annotation Type Prior


  • @Documented
 @Qualifier
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface Prior
    An extraordinarily special-purpose Qualifier annotation that may be used only to qualify a parameter in an observer method that meets the following criteria:
    1. The observer method's observed event type is an instance of HasMetadata.
    2. The observer method's observed event type parameter is qualified either directly with KubernetesEventSelector or with an annotation on which KubernetesEventSelector appears.
    3. The type of the parameter in question is a parameterized type whose raw type is Optional and whose sole actual type argument is identical to the observer method's observed event type.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson
